Thank you, Vince.

00:14:33.950 --> 00:14:36.510
When I stand up before
you, I feel a little bit

00:14:36.510 --> 00:14:41.670
like a man who owned a
business on fortune telling

00:14:41.670 --> 00:14:44.430
and had a few
